name: Steve Hobbs
tweet: "[Secretary of State Steve Hobbs] has outlined his and his agency’s plans to protect and strengthen public trust in the state and county-run election systems, focusing on three areas: Security operations... Information integrity... and Equity in voter outreach..."

name: Steve Hobbs
tweet: The Secretary of State manages the Washington State Archives. This week I had the honor of viewing the orginal 1889 Constitution of the state of Washington and reading the section establishing the Office of Secretary of State.

name: Steve Hobbs
tweet: David was an eternal optimist, a matchless combination of perceptive and sincere. I could always count on David to raise my spirits while he offered thoughtful, actionable insight. I will miss him dearly.

name: Steve Hobbs
tweet: In a February report, WA State Auditor Pat McCarthy identified an increased likelihood of ballot rejection among certain voter groups.  Those disparities are unacceptable and I am taking immediate steps to address them.  https://t.co/FX6RzmRSSC

name: Steve Hobbs
tweet: My thanks to Senator @bhasegawa for bringing forward the resolution marking the anniversary of Executive Order 9066, which allowed the forced internment of Japanese Americans 80 years ago.  I was invited to share in this moment of reflection on the Senate Floor earlier today.

name: Steve Hobbs
tweet: Election officials are on the frontline of defending democracy. Secretaries of State must be experts in cybersecurity, and fighting disinformation from organized, malicious actors.  As your chief elections officer, the protection of our election system is my highest priority.

name: Steve Hobbs
tweet: The Veterans Legislative Coalition serves those who served.  It was truly special to spend time with them today, and it is my humble honor to work with these heroes.

name: Steve Hobbs
tweet: ICYMI in this Sunday's @thecolumbian:  "Hobbs aims to stamp out lies; Election falsehoods in secretary of state's sights"  https://t.co/nJBanrvdan

name: Steve Hobbs
tweet: Today I signed the certificate of appointment for my good friend Senator @JohnLovickForWA, who replaced me as the state senator of the 44th Legislative District.   Good luck, John! You're going to do great.

name: Steve Hobbs
tweet: Protecting our democracy requires abiding vigilance, dedication and sacrifice. As your Secretary of State, I will always champion honest, transparent, accountable Democratic elections, and I will steadfastly safeguard our process from domestic and international threats.

name: Steve Hobbs
tweet: In my 33 years of military service, which includes overseas deployments, I witnessed firsthand and participated in the challenge of breathing life into a democracy. That's why I know we can't ever forget what happened in our country on January 6th.
